Description: terminal EPUB/PDF reader with Vim-style navigation
 Bookokrat is a fast terminal UI reader for EPUB and PDF documents.
 It features a split layout with a library/TOC panel on the left and
 the document reader on the right.
 .
 Features include:
  - EPUB and PDF support (optional DJVU via feature flag)
  - Vim-style keybindings and normal mode
  - Inline comments and annotations with persistent YAML storage
  - Full-text search, bookmarks, jump list navigation, and reading history
  - Image rendering, syntax-highlighted code blocks, and MathML support
  - Base16 theme selection with custom theme support
  - Adjustable margins and distraction-free zen mode
  - High-performance PDF rendering via Kitty graphics protocol
